2:T72e,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Jasper better than Longshot AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Jasper scores 8.0 overall while Longshot AI scores 6.0. Jasper is best for marketing teams and ad copy, while Longshot AI excels for fact-checked content and SEO articles."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Jasper or Longshot AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Jasper starts at $49/mo and Longshot AI starts at $19/mo.  Longshot AI offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Jasper to Longshot AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Jasper and Longshot AI support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Jasper vs Longshot AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Jasper holds an overall rating of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Longshot AI has an overall rating of 6/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise Jasper for 50+ templates for marketing use cases and Longshot AI for unique fact-checking and citation features."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Jasper or Longshot AI?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Jasper for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Longshot AI remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize unique fact-checking and citation features. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html"