7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Jasper and Longshot AI share a solid foundation of core features including Long Form, Short Form, Seo Tools, Templates. Where Jasper pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Multilingual and Api Access and Browser Extension, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Jasper holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Longshot AI scores 6/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Longshot AI comes in at a lower starting price of $19/mo, while Jasper begins at $49/mo. Longshot AI stands out by offering a free plan, giving you a risk-free way to explore the platform. Jasper requires a paid subscription from the start."}]]}]
